1 A RESOLUTION
2 To commend the Gibsland-Coleman High School boys basketball team on winning the
3 Louisiana High School Athletic Association 2026 Class C state championship.
4 WHEREAS, the Gibsland-Coleman Bulldogs boys basketball team captured the 2026
5 Class C state title by defeating Pleasant Hill, 84-83, in an overtime thriller championship
6 game; and
7 WHEREAS, De'Avery Durham led the Bulldogs with forty-eight points, including
8 forty-two scored in the second half, and received Most Outstanding Player honors; and
9 WHEREAS, Demarquis Durham also contributed twenty-four points for the
10 Bulldogs; and
11 WHEREAS, the Gibsland-Coleman Bulldogs boys basketball team is deserving of
12 recognition for its outstanding season.
13 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
14 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend the Gibsland-Coleman High School boys
15 basketball team on winning the Louisiana High School Athletic Association 2026 Class C
16 state championship and does hereby encourage the members of the team to continue their
17 excellent work and always strive for greatness in competition.
